<A>__{the same shot that night taylor's car pulls into frame. he gets out and goes up the steps. there's one light on in the apartment window. taylor comes up to the door and knocks. getting no answer, he pushes it open to find that the apartment is completely empty. just bare hardwood floor. taylor stands forlorn in the center of the room a beat, then walks on out, switching off the overhead light as he goes.}
